    } else {
        final_color = center; // Original sprite color.
    }

    return final_color;
}
```

In this modification, `is_edge` is still the boolean result from the outline detection logic, as defined in the earlier shader code. If `is_edge` is true, we set the `final_color` to the outline color; otherwise, we use the color sampled from the center of the sprite.
